## Paypal

For your convenience Zwiebelfreunde e.V. provides a PayPal gateway for donations to Tails. If possible, use Euro as currency as this will make accounting easier. However, Paypal will automatically convert it to your local currency. The email address used for donations at Paypal is <code>donate at torservers.net</code>.

